Package com.platformer.escape_beyond.model.game

Class EntityCreator

java.lang.Object
com.platformer.escape_beyond.model.game.EntityCreator
public class EntityCreator extends Object
Utility class for creating game entities dynamically.

Implements the Factory Design Pattern to centralize the creation of various entities (e.g., players, platforms, obstacles, supplies, and enemies) with their associated images.

  • Method Details

    • createEntity

      public static Entity createEntity(String entityType, int x, int y, int w, int h, int tag)
      Creates an entity object with a specified tag. The tag differentiates variations of the same entity type.
      Parameters:
      entityType - The type of entity.
      x - The x-coordinate of the entity.
      y - The y-coordinate of the entity.
      w - The width of the entity.
      h - The height of the entity.
      tag - The variation tag for the entity (default is 1).
      Returns:
      The created Entity.

    • loadImageView

      public static javafx.scene.image.Image loadImageView(String entityType, int tag)
      Loads an image for the specified entity type and tag.
      Parameters:
      entityType - The type of entity.
      tag - The variation tag for the entity.
      Returns:
      The Image corresponding to the entity type and tag.
